      "en": "A printed bed cradles the target phone beneath the gantry. Two 1020 cross-beams carry the bed and hang it under the frame, screen facing up toward the stylus.",
      "zh": "目标手机搁在龙门架下方一个打印件托架里。两根 1020 横梁托住托架，将其吊装在框架下方，屏幕朝上正对触控笔。"
    }
